folder: Willow St. & Pierrepont St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Willow Street, west side, north from Pierrepont Street, showing in the foreground, the Fisher house built in 1832. (It was demolished to make way for an apartment building in 1929).

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
